So I have to say, I'm kind of curious, why the sudden friend request?  I haven't talked to you in like, what, three years?  Definitely not trying to sound like a bitch, I was just curious.  How're things going?  You still in Flag?

Brian
I'm good, I think I saw you in the friend suggestion because other people I am friends with are friends with you.  I usually add all people I know or have met, not necessarily good friends with.  Still living in Flagstaff about to start my 5th year, doing pretty well.  How are you?

I'm alright, still in Flag as well.  Ditto on the 5th year part, but luckily it's the last so I can be done finally!  Can't wait to leave Flag though, I absolutely dread having pretty much nothing to do.  Oh, by the way, way jealous of all the traveling!

Brian
Yeah, it's been great; sick of planes though. Flagstaff is pretty low key.  I'm glad to see I'm not the only one taking it easy on the degree progress.  Good luck with your last year!
Yeah you too!  I'm definitely a fan of taking my time school-wise. haha
